data.description: Seller to contribute $10,000 towards closing cost or buydown rate.  Two-story brick residence has a finished basement hosting a 25 x 24 recreation room, an ideal spot for game days and gatherings. 6 bedrooms and 5 baths have ample space for family and guests. 21ft vaulted ceiling in living room and 18ft ceiling in foyer. You will enjoy the convenience of a tankless water heater. The large eat-in kitchen features a large island. All this plus a three-car garage, offers the perfect blend of comfort, and functionality. Nestled on a spacious lot, fenced backyard with mature trees and a full deck. Just 15 minutes from Redstone Arsenal. All facts TBV
